        "question": "What should I expect during my first visit?",
        "answer": "During your first visit to Northside Physio Care, one of our experienced physiotherapists will conduct a thorough assessment of your condition. We will discuss your treatment goals and create a personalized physiotherapy treatment plan tailored specifically for you."
      },
