        "question": "Are the treatment plans personalized?",
        "answer": "Absolutely! Each treatment plan at Northside Physio Care is customized based on your unique needs and recovery goals. We believe that personalized care is key to effective physiotherapy and achieving the best outcomes."
      },
      {
        "question": "How does physiotherapy help with pain management?",
        "answer": "Physiotherapy is an evidence-based practice that helps in pain management through various techniques such as manual therapy, exercise prescription, and education. Our physiotherapists will work closely with you to alleviate pain and improve your mobility, helping you return to your daily activities."
      },
      {
        "question": "What are common physiotherapy myths debunked?",
        "answer": "Many people believe that physiotherapy is only for athletes or those recovering from surgery. In reality, physiotherapy can benefit anyone experiencing pain or mobility issues, including families and seniors. Our team is here to clarify treatment doubts and guide you on the right path to recovery."
